,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cdfca5a6f08c71f03485e4183261ed43540d753","tid":1217513,"uid":240628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴霧必須用品<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OeDsoU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OeDsoU</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8aef761011d109c498361855a99160403139ef","tid":1217513,"uid":126612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"【開始有疲態】星期日再遊行可唔可以有新形式呢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240540</a><br />\n<br />\n直接圍堵無咁大號召力<br />\n用「遊行」呢個名義係召集到最多人<br />\n隊頭行到政總，即刻成條到維園條隊一齊坐低<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暫緩</span></span></strong>遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSet 8點 deadline 回應訴求<br />\n大家唔使行，有得抖，旁邊商鋪餐廳廁所隨時有得用<br />\n<br />\n8點唔回應就可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重啓</span></span></strong>遊行，改地點去禮賓府！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相鼓勵和理非一齊「衝」、「圍」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2418918adb5db7b5d767438732f1f93a9f84f237","tid":1217513,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"我地要星期五出黎約打網球"},{"pid":"14d3176ef3192860a96e0cbdb7cc037ce65cbd5